					<a href="/about/contact" class="group inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-gray-300 text-base font-medium rounded-full text-gray-700 bg-white hover:border-[#54C4B6] hover:text-[#54C4B6] transition-all duration-300">
						Contact Us
